---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import SectionBanner from '../../components/ui/SectionBanner.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Large-Scale Projects"
  description="Airport terminals, urban masterplans, infrastructure corridors. Vision Graphics Kft. — Budapest-based, working globally since 1996."
>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-large-scale.jpg"
    label="Large-Scale Projects"
    title="Visualize Complex Developments"
    size="page"
    headingLevel="h1"
  />
  <div class="service-page">

    <div class="service-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/services/">Services</a>
      <span>→</span>
      <span>Large-Scale Projects</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Service</p>
    <h2 class="display-lg service-h1">Large-Scale Projects</h2>
    <p class="service-tagline-large">Big projects need a studio that's done it before.</p>

    <div class="service-body-grid">
      <div class="service-main">

        <p class="service-lead">
          Big projects need clear visuals. Over three decades, we've helped clients turn complex
          plans into visuals that make sense to everyone — from city planners to the public.
          Their complexity demands visualization that combines technical precision with narrative
          clarity to drive understanding and action.
        </p>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">Notable past work</h2>
        <div class="notable-grid">
          {[
            { name: 'Budapest Airport — Terminal 2B', year: '1996 & 2009' },
            { name: 'Antalya Airport — Terminal 2', year: '2023–2024' },
            { name: 'Sochi Airport', year: '2006–2008' },
            { name: 'Pulkovo Airport', year: '2006–2008' },
            { name: 'Road Safety Centre, Doha', year: '2012–2014' },
            { name: 'Mol Campus, Budapest', year: '2015–2017' },
            { name: 'Hungexpo, Budapest', year: '2018–2021' },
            { name: 'Agora Budapest', year: '2021' },
          ].map(p => (
            <div class="notable-item">
              <span class="notable-name">{p.name}</span>
              <span class="notable-year">{p.year}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Pricing</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-price">Custom</p>
          <p class="sidebar-note">Scoped individually to your project. Quote within one business day of receiving materials.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-cta">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary sidebar-btn">Talk to Us</a>
          <a href="/portfolio/?cat=airport,infrastructure,urban" class="btn btn-ghost">See portfolio</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-arch-viz.jpg"
    label="Urban Development"
    title="Cities in Motion"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">Cities are always changing. We help you show people what's coming and why it matters. When a city's changing, people have questions — good visuals give them answers before they even ask, speeding up approvals and getting everyone on board faster.</p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Clear views of how new buildings fit into neighbourhoods</li>
      <li>Virtual tours so people can explore future spaces</li>
      <li>Time-lapse views showing how the project will roll out</li>
      <li>Environmental impact visuals that make technical data easy to grasp</li>
      <li>Real-world simulations of traffic and people moving through spaces</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-general.jpg"
    label="Infrastructure"
    title="Complex Made Clear"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">Roads, bridges, and railways keep cities moving. Explaining these projects can be tricky. We break down complex infrastructure into clear visuals that help planners make better decisions and show the public why changes are worth it.</p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>How construction will happen, step by step</li>
      <li>Where new projects connect with existing ones</li>
      <li>How traffic will keep flowing during construction</li>
      <li>What the environmental impact will be</li>
      <li>How the finished project will benefit everyone</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-large-scale.jpg"
    label="Airport Projects"
    title="Airports Never Stop"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">Airports are like small cities that never stop. They need to grow and change without disrupting operations. We help spot problems early — when they're still cheap to fix — and show how to keep the airport running smoothly while building for the future.</p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Phased construction visualization — show how to build without disrupting flights</li>
      <li>Passenger flow simulations that test new layouts</li>
      <li>Interior design visuals for choosing the best options</li>
      <li>Interactive comparisons of different design choices</li>
      <li>Clear wayfinding and signage visualization</li>
      <li>Security and operations planning</li>
      <li>Future expansion scenarios</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-workflow.jpg"
    label="Industrial"
    title="Factories That Work"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">Factories and production spaces need to work efficiently. We help plan these spaces and show people how to use them. Our animated training materials help workers understand new setups quickly — they can see exactly how processes should work, making training more effective and reducing mistakes.</p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Factory layout planning that optimises space</li>
      <li>Machine placement visuals that show how everything fits</li>
      <li>Animated process workflows for packaging and manufacturing</li>
      <li>Safety and emergency route planning</li>
      <li>Interactive training materials for workers</li>
      <li>Future expansion options</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</Page>

<style>
  .service-page {
    max-width: 1060px;
    padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .service-breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 200ms; }
  .service-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .service-h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-tagline-large { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h6); font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-lead { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .service-body-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .service-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .service-section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .notable-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .notable-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); gap: 1rem; transition: background 200ms; }
  .notable-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .notable-item:hover { background: var(--color-surface); }
  .notable-name { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .notable-year { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); white-space: nowrap; }

  /* Sub-sections */
  .service-section { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }

  .section-body { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .results-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .results-list li { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .results-list li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-accent); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }

  /* Sidebar */
  .service-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 5rem; }
  .sidebar-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .sidebar-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .sidebar-price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h5); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-note { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-body-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .service-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
